  from [[sicmutils.env]] into your REPL:

  ```clojure
  (require '[sicmutils.env :as e])
  (e/bootstrap-repl!)
  ```

  Or, in Clojure:

  ```clojure
  (require '[sicmutils.env :as e :refer :all])
